                     <interp inst="t17901027-34-verdict179" type="verdictSubcategory" value="theftunder5s"></interp>
               GUILTY, value 4 s
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t17901027-34-punish180" type="punishmentDescription">
